     FINPUT   IP  F    9999            DISK
     FVJBWP18 O   F    9999            DISK
     E                    SK         99  1               ﾅhﾆﾞﾑﾃ-nﾞ bk
     IINPUT   AA  01
     I                                        19999 IREC
     I                                        1  99 SK
     I                                        1   1 ISKJY
     I                                        2   7 ISKHZ
     I            DS
     I                                        1   30UH
     I            DS
     I                                        1   60SHIZK
     I                                        1   1 US1
     I                                        2   2 US2
     I                                        3   3 US3
     I                                        4   4 US4
     I                                        5   5 US5
     I                                        6   6 US6
     C           *ENTRY    PLIST
     C                     PARM           PNUKI   6
     C                     PARM           PRECD   7
     C                     PARM           PKENS   7
     C                     PARM           PSKHI   3
     C                     PARM           PFILE   7
      *
     C           *IN02     IFEQ '0'
     C                     SETON                     02
     C                     MOVE PNUKI     UNUKI   60
     C                     MOVE PSKHI     UH
      *
     C                     MOVE UH        I1      20
     C           UH        ADD  1         I2      20
     C           UH        ADD  2         I3      20
     C           UH        ADD  3         I4      20
     C           UH        ADD  4         I5      20
     C           UH        ADD  5         I6      20
     C                     END
      *
     C                     ADD  1         WRECD   70
      *
     C                     MOVE SK,I1     US1
     C                     MOVE SK,I2     US2
     C                     MOVE SK,I3     US3
     C                     MOVE SK,I4     US4
     C                     MOVE SK,I5     US5
     C                     MOVE SK,I6     US6
      *
     C           PFILE     IFNE 'AAJPP11'
     C                     MOVE ISKHZ     WSKHZ   60
      *
     C           ISKJY     IFEQ 'D'
     C           WSKHZ     ANDLEUDATE
     C                     GOTO END
     C                     END
     C                     END
      *
     C           SHIZK     IFGT UNUKI
     C                     ADD  1         WKENS   70
     C                     EXCPTDT
     C                     END
      *
     C           END       TAG
      *
     CLR                   MOVE WRECD     PRECD
     CLR                   MOVE WKENS     PKENS
      *
     OVJBWP18 E                DT
